{"title":"[CW]Faberge easter eggs crush test题解(数学部分)","uid":"01937456cef72f998b8b619fdd155a88","slug":"CW-Faberge-easter-eggs-crush-test","date":"2020-06-27T13:34:50.000Z","updated":"2020-06-27T13:34:50.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CW-Faberge-easter-eggs-crush-test.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"递推式\"><a href=\"#递推式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"递推式\"></a>递推式</h2><p>按照题意，若设所求函数为<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(n,m)</annotation></semantics></math></span>，则有：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{aligned}\n  F(0,m)&amp;=0\\\\\n  F(n,0)&amp;=0\\\\\n  F(n,m)&amp;=F(n,m-1)+F(n-1,m-1)+1\n\\end{aligned}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<h2 id=\"生成函数\"><a href=\"#生成函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"生成函数\"></a>生成函数</h2><p>注意到其生成函数满足</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">G(x,y)=yG(x,y)+xyG(x,y)+\\frac{xy}{(1-x)(1-y)}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<p>移项可得：</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{aligned}\n  (1-y-xy)G(x,y)&amp;=\\frac{xy}{(1-x)(1-y)} \\\\\n  G(x,y)&amp;=y(1-y)^{-1}x(1-x)^{-1}(1-y-xy)^{-1}\\\\\n\\end{aligned}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<h2 id=\"解生成函数\"><a href=\"#解生成函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解生成函数\"></a>解生成函数</h2><p>令: <span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p_1=(1-x)^{-1},p_2=(1-y-xy)^{-1}</annotation></semantics></math></span></p>\n<p>则: <span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mi>x</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">G(x,y)=y(1-y)^{-1}xp_1p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span></p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mi>x</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mrow></mfrac><mspace linebreak=\"newline\"></mspace><msub><mrow><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo fence=\"true\">∣</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><msub><mrow><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mi>x</mi><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo fence=\"true\">∣</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\frac {\\partial^n G(x,y)} {\\partial x^n}\n= y(1-y)^{-1}\\frac { \\partial^nxp_1p_2 } {\\partial x^n}\\\\\n\\left. \\frac{\\partial^n G(x,y)}{\\partial x^n} \\right| _{x=0}\n= y(1-y)^{-1}\\left.\\frac{ \\partial^nxp_1p_2 }{\\partial x^n}\\right| _{x=0}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<h3 id=\"莱布尼兹法则\"><a href=\"#莱布尼兹法则\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"莱布尼兹法则\"></a>莱布尼兹法则</h3><p>注意如下同构</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mtext>令</mtext><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mi>m</mi></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>∼</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>v</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mi>m</mi></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mi>m</mi></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>∼</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>v</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>v</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>v</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo mathvariant=\"normal\" lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">′</mo></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>0</mn></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>0</mn></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></munderover><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo></mrow></mfrac><msup><mi>a</mi><mi>i</mi></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>∼</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mi>v</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></munderover><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo></mrow></mfrac><msup><mi>u</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup><msup><mi>v</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\begin{aligned}\n令a^nb^m &amp;\\sim u^{(n)}v^{(m)} \\\\\na^nb^m(a+b)=a^{n+1}b^m+a^nb^{m+1} &amp;\n\\sim u^{(n+1)}v^{(m)}+u^{(n)}v^{(m+1)}=(u^{(n)}v^{(m)})&#x27; \\\\\na^0b^0(a+b)^n=\\sum_{i=0}^n \\frac {n!} {i!(n-i)!} a^ib^{n-i}&amp;\n\\sim (uv)^{(n)}=\\sum_{i=0}^n \\frac {n!} {i!(n-i)!} u^{(i)}v^{(n-i)} \\\\\n\\end{aligned}</annotation></semantics></math></span>\n<h3 id=\"处理p1p2p-1p-2\"><a href=\"#处理p1p2p-1p-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"处理p1p2p_1p_2\"></a>处理<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p_1p_2</annotation></semantics></math></span></h3><p>解出</p>\n<span class=\"katex\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mrow></mfrac></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">!</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><msub><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"norm